{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-038","title":"Sentence 38","sectionId":"sentences-031","sectionTitle":"Sentence 31-40","pageStart":255,"pageEnd":263,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":45,"duplicateEntryCount":6,"pages":[{"number":255,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 38"},{"type":"text","text":"The elimination of inflation would ensure that the amount of money"},{"type":"text","text":"used in repaying a loan would have the same value as the amount of"},{"type":"text","text":"money borrowed."},{"type":"text","text":"消除通货膨胀，可确保用来偿还贷款的钱与借贷的钱价值相"},{"type":"text","text":"等。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是“The elimination of inflation would ensure that ...”，其"},{"type":"text","text":"中that引导一个宾语从句。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"elimination /ɪˌlɪmɪˈneɪʃn/ n. 消除，除去","headword":"elimination"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 e（除去）+limin（限制）+ation（表名词）→消除对事物的"},{"type":"text","text":"限制→消除"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 eliminate vt. 消除；淘汰"},{"type":"entry","text":"inflation /ɪnˈfleɪʃn/ n. 膨胀；通货膨胀","headword":"inflation"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 currency inflation 通货膨胀"},{"type":"note","text":"反义 deflation n. 通货紧缩"},{"type":"entry","text":"ensure /ɪnˈʃʊr/ vt. 确保，担保","headword":"ensure"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 en（使…）+sur（确定的）+e→确保"},{"type":"note","text":"参考 assure vt. 确保；使确信"}]},{"number":256,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"insure vt. 给…保险"},{"type":"entry","text":"repay /rɪˈpeɪ/ v. 偿还，归还","headword":"repay"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 repay a loan 还清贷款"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 repayment n. 偿还债务"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"与“货币发行与流通”相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"currency /ˈkɜːrənsi/ n. 货币","headword":"currency"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 currency exchange 货币兑换"},{"type":"text","text":"credit currency 信用货币"},{"type":"text","text":"currency circulation 货币流通"},{"type":"text","text":"currency issue 货币发行"},{"type":"entry","text":"defla